 Galvatron floated gently into the air. And put her arms around his neck and 
picked up her legs with his left arm. "Im glad you decided to come. To my 
destron base. Its cloaked which give us a  little bit of an advantage." He 
shook his head inside. Magnus's feelings were overpowering him. He thought 
since he had shed his spark that his pollutients would be gone....but he was 
wrong. He knew of her energon as Magnus did. A useful tool for his group. 
Hopefully when her memoried fully returned. Her impression of his name 
wouldnt make her run scared. Hed have to influence her while he could. He 
went full blast towards the destron base.

--part1_ea.19c99bf9.28ab43ba_boundary
